\end_inset

增加时，卡尔曼增益矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{K}_{k}$
\end_inset

接近零：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{K}_{k}=\boldsymbol{P}_{k}^{-}\boldsymbol{H}_{k}^{\mathrm{T}}\left(\boldsymbol{Q}_{v,k}\right)^{-1}=\boldsymbol{0}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

